bilingual.target: 这是一个阳光明媚的早晨。

bilingual.source: It was a Sunday morning in April.
bilingual.target: 那是四月的一个星期天早晨。

bilingual.source: It was the usual hectic Monday morning.
bilingual.target: 这是一个平常忙碌的星期一早晨。

bilingual.source: It was sunny, but the ground was wet from rain in the morning.
bilingual.target: 天气晴朗，但地面因早晨的雨水而湿滑。

bilingual.source: Breakfast is important because it gives us energy for the morning.
bilingual.target: 早餐很重要，因为它给我们早晨提供能量。

bilingual.source: On midsummer's morning, the sun shines directly into the center of the stones.
bilingual.target: 在仲夏的早晨，阳光直射到石头的中心。

bilingual.source: So early one cold winter morning, she set out to a distant town.
bilingual.target: 所以在一个寒冷的冬天早晨，她出发前往一个遥远的小镇。

bilingual.source: Instead of being printed, the Earth Chronicle is every morning spoken to subscribers.
bilingual.target: 《地球纪事》每天早晨通过语音传达给订阅者。

bilingual.source: Then, on the morning of my birthday, I woke up to find a beautiful violin at my bedside.
bilingual.target: 然后，在我生日的早晨，我醒来发现床边有一把漂亮的小提琴。
牵牛花在早晨开得最美。

list.abstract: morning（英[ˈmɔːnɪŋ]，美[ˈmɔːrnɪŋ]），英语单词，作名词为上午；早晨；破晓。作副词为每天早晨。作惊叹词为早上好。短语搭配有tomorrow morning（明天早晨）。例句为“Edward rose early on the New-year morning.（新年的早晨，爱德华早早起床了）”。 morning名词类近义词有prime、sunrise，相关反义词有sunset。

《Morning》是香港歌手卫兰于2009年7月3日发行的专辑。Janice 在2005年凭翻唱黎明金曲「我这样爱你」和「情深说话未曾讲」的英文版而走红，转眼间推出了四张专辑。继去年《Serving You》，Janice 回归音乐的最基本，以她最擅长唱的英文歌唱出自我。 《Morning》是 Janice 出道以来首张全英文歌专辑，十首原创英文歌的曲风由爵士乐、法式惰怀、骚灵、摇滚至田园小品不等。主打歌「Rainbow」由新加坡音乐人Taz为她度身订做，以彩虹的七彩颜色来传达爱的讯息，Janice 在曲中演绎高音部分，尽显功架。碟内亦收录了她较早前为为宣扬毒害的讯息的禁毒歌曲「999」，曲中以节奏强劲令青少年有所共鸣。

yingyinNormal.en: Morning hugs! Give me my morning hugs. No, gross! Daddy, you're all sweaty.
yingyinNormal.zh: 早晨的抱抱。给我个早晨的抱抱。不，你太脏了。爸爸，你浑身都是汗。

yingyinNormal.en: And when the first tourists start to arrive in the morning, I begin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 早晨第一批游客抵达时，我开始表演。

yingyinNormal.en: It is a lovely sunny morning. And Daddy Pig is reading his newspaper.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天是个阳光明媚的早晨。猪爸爸正在看他的报纸。

yingyinNormal.en: It is a lovely sunny morning. Daddy Pig is driving to work in his car.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天是个阳光明媚的早晨。猪爸爸开着车去上班了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, dear god. I'm sorry, I didn't realize I was interrupting your morning prayers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 上帝啊。对不起，我不是故意来打扰你做早晨祷告。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, the next morning, I woke up, I looked out the window and Walter was still up in that tree.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第二天早晨，我醒来，往窗外一看，沃特还在树上。

yingyinNormal.en: Unacceptable. The delay would result in tomorrow morning's bowel movement occurring at work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不予通过，吃饭太晚会造成明天早晨的大肠蠕动出现在工作时间。

yingyinNormal.en: Morning. It's morning, everyone! Today's the day! The sun is shining. The tank is clean and we are getting out. The tank is clean.
yingyinNormal.zh: 早，是早晨了，大家! 今天就是那个逃亡日! 阳光明媚，鱼缸乾净了，我们就要出去了。鱼缸乾净了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, Dr. And Mrs. Hofstadter, lovely to see you this fine morning. You're in a good mood. Yeah, I am indeed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 霍夫斯塔德博士贤伉俪，在这美好的早晨，很高兴见到两位。你心情很好啊。的确是的。

yingyinNormal.en: Last week, he brought this girl over and I started talking to her about morning sickness and then I showed her pictures from my pregnancy book.
yingyinNormal.zh: 上星期他带一个女孩回家，我跟她谈早晨呕吐的问题，还把我怀孕纪念册的照片拿给她看。

yingyinNormal.en: Our royal family will attend the private services in St. James's palace the morning of with 28 other heads of state from all over the globe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 皇室成员当天早晨会在圣詹姆斯宫参加一个私人拜会，其余28位各国首脑届时也会一同出席。

yingyinNormal.en: Beautiful early morning in Hong Kong and I am heading out to the barge, which is where Wilson and his crew are working, setting up all the fireworks in preparation for the display.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是香港早晨，我前往驳船去见在那里工作的威尔森和他的队员们，他们在放置所有准备表演的烟花。

yingyinNormal.en: It is the last morning of Peppa's holiday in Italy. I'm just going for one last walk. Going for one last swim, Mr. Pig? Yes. One last swim before I go home.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是佩奇在意大利的假期的最后一个早晨。我要最后再散步一次。去游最后一次泳吗，猪先生？是的，在我回家之前最后游一次。

yingyinNormal.en: It is the last morning of Peppa's holiday in Italy. I'm just going for one last walk. Going for one last swim, Mr. Pig? Yes. One last swim before I go home.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是佩奇在意大利的假期的最后一个早晨。我要最后再散步一次。去游最后一次泳吗，猪先生？是的，在我回家之前最后游一次。

yingyinNormal.en: Morning. Morning. Morning. How'd you sleep? All right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 早啊。早。早。睡得好吗？还行吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Hi. Good morning, Dave. Good morning. Hi.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗨，早上好，戴夫。早上好，嗨。

yingyinNormal.en: Good morning, wife. Good morning, husband.
yingyinNormal.zh: 早安啊，老婆。早安啊，老公。

yingyinNormal.en: Good morning, Mrs. Florrick. Good morning to you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 早上好，福瑞克夫人。早上好。

yingyinNormal.en: Morning. Morning. You're making eggs for breakfast?
yingyinNormal.zh: 早。今天早餐你做鸡蛋吃？

yingyinNormal.en: Morning, daddy. You sleep well?
yingyinNormal.zh: 早上好，爸爸，睡得好吗？

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: As somebody who got up every <highlight>morning</highlight> at seven to practice, that experience changed me and made me part of who I am today.

例如: She plays the piano mornings.

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Macy walks there with him every <highlight>morning</highlight> unless the weather is bad.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 除非天气不好，梅西每天早上都和他步行去那里。

examination_example.sentence: Working out in the <highlight>morning</highlight> provides additional benefits beyond being physically fit.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 除了保持身体健康，早上锻炼还能带来额外的好处。

examination_example.sentence: Lots of people find it hard to get up in the <highlight>morning</highlight> and put the blame on the alarm clock.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 很多人发现早上很难起床，并将责任归咎于闹钟。

examination_example.sentence: One <highlight>morning</highlight>, I had to book an immediate flight home for a family emergency.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一天早上，我因为家里有急事，不得不订了最近一班回家的航班。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: In the <highlight>morning</highlight>, we go to our school at 8:45.
Though it seldom rains in summer, it sometimes drizzles on early winter <highlight>mornings</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 虽然夏天很少下雨，但冬天的早晨有时会下毛毛雨。

examination_example.sentence: The next <highlight>morning</highlight>, when he opened his mouth to say "Good <highlight>morning</highlight>", nothing came out but a croak.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 第二天早上，当他张开嘴说“早上好”时，除了一声呱呱声外，什么也没说出来。
